 420                 AddLocalVariable(AttrOrVar(ToUtf32("Specifiers"), ToUtf32("specifiers")));
 421                 AddLocalVariable(AttrOrVar(ToUtf32("bool"), ToUtf32("functionDeclarator")));
 422             }
 423             public override void Enter(Stack<UniquePtr<Object>>& stack, ParsingData* parsingData)
 424             {
 425                 parsingData->PushContext(Id(), new Context());
 426                 Context* context = cast<Context*>(parsingData->GetContext(Id()));
 427                 UniquePtr<Object> accessSpecifier_value = stack.Pop();
 428                 context->accessSpecifier = *cast<ValueObject<Specifiers>*>(accessSpecifier_value.Get());
 429                 UniquePtr<Object> ctx_value = stack.Pop();
 430                 context->ctx = *cast<ValueObject<ParsingContext*>*>(ctx_value.Get());
 431             }
 432             public override void Leave(Stack<UniquePtr<Object>>& stack, ParsingData* parsingData, bool matched)
 433             {
 434                 Context* context = cast<Context*>(parsingData->GetContext(Id()));
 435                 if (matched)
 436                 {
 437                     stack.Push(UniquePtr<Object>(new ValueObject<Node*>(context->value)));
 438                 }
 439                 parsingData->PopContext(Id());
 440             }
